### 16 · Collection UI

<div class="not-prose flex gap-2 mb-3">
  <span class="font-mono text-xs bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">TypeScript</span>
